{"word":"ὑποκλέπτω","slug":"ὑποκλέπτω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ὑποκλέπτω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>ψω</el>) </el><p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to steal underhand, filch</i>, <b><a href='S:Babrius'>Babr.</a></b>: —<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to be stolen away</i>, <b><a href='S:Pindar'>Pind.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><el>ὑποκλέπτεσθαί τι</el> <i>to be defrauded of</i> a thing, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}